{"tid":2215080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 馬道立反撃左報 「司法機構不容政治化」","createTime":"2020-09-23T17:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T18:28:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2cacfecf5dd2373fdbffa6b24751074d056d6d05","tid":2215080,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/120110588_10159474312752448_2639571997571147533_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=_trOIxXzNb0AX-dognW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=de0880a0b6f83262cce4536cab96761e&amp;oe=5F91AC7E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F120110588_10159474312752448_2639571997571147533_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D_trOIxXzNb0AX-dognW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26tp%3D7%26oh%3Dde0880a0b6f83262cce4536cab96761e%26oe%3D5F91AC7E&h=7dfb4fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【A1頭條】近期本港法院遭左報及建制派文革式口誅筆伐 ，批評法官屢「 輕判暴徒 」， 親共陣營更發起一人一信投訴施壓。將於明年1月退休的終審法院首席法官馬道立，昨罕有地發表長達 14 頁的聲明，強調司法機構絕不應被政治化，認為對法官或法院的批評須有理有據，反擊有人單憑「 純粹聲稱或斷章取義之事 」 批評法官，或因案件結果不合心意而作出嚴重指稱均屬錯誤。法律界認為馬道立聲明反映目前情況嚴峻，必須正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.10150161306277448/10159474312747448/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.10150161306277448%2F10159474312747448%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=b53316c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.10150161306277448/10159474312747448/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"47109ad556a560df45ccf6c9b0e2b20e291a9f84","tid":2215080,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil